{"tid":1143383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（鑑証實録）休班鑑證科警長涉乘小巴胸襲17歲少女被捕","createTime":"2019-05-07T16:46:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T01:26:30.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"21aef969304ee1806e052ef5237ba36f084da9ab","tid":1143383,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:46:21.000Z","msg":"(4日)晚上11時許，荃灣一輛小巴上疑發生非禮案，一名54歲休班男警長在荃灣青山公路青龍頭上車，疑向坐於前排座椅17歲少女摸胸，少女高呼非禮，驚動司機及車內乘客，於是報警，少女指遭人在後座位與車窗罅隙間伸手摸胸。<br />\n<br />\n警方調查期間，發現涉案男子為隸屬鑑證科警長，在指模房工作，警方以涉嫌非禮罪將他拘捕。涉案警長已獲准保釋，須於5月下旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2343106\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2343106&d=702bRGgXdrZysJ%2FhnUM8SxPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=2fdc2ff1\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2343106</a>"},{"pid":"733e2240df506c3500162314df38d1d087c26f58","tid":1143383,"uid":108201,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:47:26.000Z","msg":"高層震怒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7733474e1dccead5dacee47b713226d2603c67ef","tid":1143383,"uid":113373,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:50:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">反對修訂逃犯條例 香港的終局之戰<br />\n不惜一切 逆轉未來</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">5月11日 星期六 早上8點半<br />\n立法會將會開會討論有關修訂 暫未知會否表決 <br />\n由於秘書處政變 原本由涂謹申主持會議改為石禮謙主持<br />\n<br />\n事態危急<br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人任何罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8f06dcfd06b345f84ccce2397faf370d390bedaf","tid":1143383,"uid":31370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:54:52.000Z","msg":"阿蛇做野⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa2c9f0f9a783a2ab7ee5ac5cf5a042b89bb379c","tid":1143383,"uid":184233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T16:59:51.000Z","msg":"17歲少女 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb8f6f9922899ce1dd887570edbcd14d7a5bc91","tid":1143383,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T01:06:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"115865f540c9e8d88e19ee1679fc553584b41ded","tid":1143383,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T01:06:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3190ef46bfc100bb20a658cecf21aed31d1981f8","tid":1143383,"uid":3457,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T01:08:23.000Z","msg":"係味佔中壓力？ 壓左咁多年 <br />\n都係佔中衰喇 <br />\n渣波又點wo～"},{"pid":"da6307ba6d4716da3d5f3b1bf6e96f624f50517a","tid":1143383,"uid":2521,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"3190ef46bfc100bb20a658cecf21aed31d1981f8","tid":1143383,"uid":3457,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T01:08:23.000Z","msg":"係味佔中壓力？ 壓左咁多年 <br />\n都係佔中衰喇 <br />\n渣波又點wo～"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T01:12:02.000Z","msg":"據聞係條女用個胸襲擊警長"},{"pid":"4701d8fb06c94da3802257ebcd298a79c05464c8","tid":1143383,"uid":237562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T01:13:07.000Z","msg":"阿sir 鑑證下條女對波堅定流啫"},{"pid":"6981d22c37a3172509ef4fc8b60120e121e30c82","tid":1143383,"uid":92385,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T01:25:01.000Z","msg":"警方調查期間，發現涉案男子為隸屬鑑證科警長，在指模房工作<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCheck下少女個胸有冇警長指模<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6bc4d63260531ebc2f963f16095f8ed09a46575","tid":1143383,"uid":4420,"l